Canonical website:
  https://github.com/tpm2-software/tpm2-pkcs11

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/tpm2-software/tpm2-pkcs11/archive/refs/tags/1.9.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack tpm2-pkcs11-1.9.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./tpm2-pkcs11-1.9.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/tpm2-pkcs11-1.9.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/tpm2-pkcs11-1.9.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtpm2_pkcs11_1-1.9.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libtpm2_pkcs11-devel-1.9.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(tpm2-pkcs11)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/tpm2-pkcs11.README
  /usr/share/doc/tpm2-pkcs11/CHANGELOG.md
  /usr/share/doc/tpm2-pkcs11/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/tpm2-pkcs11/README.md

(libtpm2_pkcs11_1)
  /usr/bin/cygtpm2_pkcs11-1.dll

(libtpm2_pkcs11-devel)
  /usr/include/pkcs11.h
  /usr/lib/libtpm2_pkcs11.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/tpm2-pkcs11.pc

